### Reg-Tech API — Authentication Endpoints
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### ─── Register a new user ───
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@celticfs.ie",
  "password": "RegTech2024!Secure",
  "firstName": "Patrick",
  "lastName": "O'Brien",
  "organizationId": "00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004"
}

###

### ─── Login ───
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "compliance@celticfs.ie",
  "password": "RegTech2024!"
}

###

### ─── Login with 2FA ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "compliance@celticfs.ie",
  "password": "RegTech2024!",
  "totpCode": "123456"
}

###

### ─── Refresh Token ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{login.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

###

### ─── Setup 2FA ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/2fa/setup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Verify 2FA ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/2fa/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "123456"
}

###

### ─── Logout ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
